channel.title: Help! This is ergent, and If I dont get this fixed, I cant put my server up
channel.description:
(I'll post my entire batch log when it crashes again, so get ready or a long post)
Every 5-30 minutes, my server just kicks everybody off, crashes, prevents people from coming online, and in the batch log, it just says "PLAYERNAME is already online". This is a ongoing problem, and, if I can't fix it, it will result in the closure of SlomiScape.
(Like I said above, I will post my log, so get ready for a long post)
(And no, this isent a anti-lag script, so don't try that.)
sorry, i did get a copy of it, than i copied over it, so I need to wait till it happens again
